# Summary
This documentation explains how to use prediction-based cohorts in marketing campaigns, covering three campaign types (Inclusion Criteria, Dynamic Pricing, Content Personalization), the process for syncing cohorts to marketing platforms, setting up control groups, and analyzing campaign results to determine effectiveness across different user segments.

